text: "The Seashores of Old Mexico" is a song by George Strait. ==Music video== The music video and premiered on March 23, 2006 on CMT. It debuted at number 20 on CMT's Top 20 Countdown for the week of April 20, 2006. The video peaked at number 1 on CMT's Top Twenty Countdown for two consecutive weeks in July 2006. ==References== Category:2005 songs Category:Music videos directed by Trey Fanjoy
